Aggregates.Name: Store
Aggregates.Definition: A place where Store Items can be purchased

CommandMethods.Name: Process Transaction
CommandMethods.Purpose: Add items to the inventory that have been purchased

ValueObjects.Name: Inventory
ValueObjects.Definition: A collection of Store Items within a store

ValueObjects.Name: Store Metadata
ValueObjects.Definition: The metadata about the store including name and website

CommandMethods.Name: Update Profile
CommandMethods.Purpose: Allow customer to update their name

CommandMethods.Name: Add Item To Cart
CommandMethods.Purpose: Add an item to the customers shopping cart

CommandMethods.Name: Remove Items From Cart
CommandMethods.Purpose: Remove all items from cart associated with the item

CommandMethods.Name: Checkout
CommandMethods.Purpose: Customer checks out of the store

ValueObjects.Name: Cart
ValueObjects.Definition: A collection of store items available for purchase

DomainEvents.Name: Customer Checkout
DomainEvents.Definition: An event indicating that the customer has checked out with the given items
